README

Disclaimer: I’m not a professional, I hack around trying to get “the” stuff to work. C is really REALLY hard. I would like feedback! and thank you!

Clone project: 
git clone https://github.com/murf0/esp_mqtt.git

Checkout Submodules:
git submodule init
git submodule update

Patch mkespfsimage:
cd lib && patch -p0 < mkespfsimage.patch && cd ..

Copy New LD file:
cp eagle.app.v6.New.ld /Volumes/esp-open-sdk/sdk/ld/

Update Submodules:
git submodule foreach git pull origin master


Build & Flash:
./build.sh

Clear out Settings (AP and such):
Write blank.bin to address 0x7e000
esptool.py -p /dev/tty.wchusbserial1410 write_flash 0x7e000 ../blank.bin

Update Submodules:
git submodule foreach git pull origin master

Issues:
Lots and lots of stuff isn't is actually working...
